---
title: Beefqueso Burgers with Spicy Crema and Kale Caesar
description: Smoky, spicy, cheesy and on the table in just 20 minutes, this burger is bound to have you looking forward to dinnertime! Simple beef patties get a blanket of creamy, melty mozzarella on top make this burger shine. If that isn't enough, we've added a lemony kale Caesar side salad to sweeten the deal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-de-boeuf-style-choriqueso-7f99c774.jpg
